{"tid":1486393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到上加拿大國會]加拿大東岸文宣全面展開","createTime":"2019-08-19T00:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T03:43:14.000Z","uid":273293,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8c84c8588eb8230e5118a04c61ea73c860db62e8","tid":1486393,"uid":273293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:49:51.000Z","msg":"我地除左尋日係Halifax 集會聲援香港 (見post <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480948</a>) 文宣工作無停過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地已經投稿東岸各大報章，電台</span></span>，包括CBC，The Chronicle Herald，The Coast ， The Telegram， 向全加拿大人宣揚港共惡行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日加拿大國營電台CBC去左我地個集會訪問，已經出左街<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/ottawa-urged-to-support-hong-kong-protesters-at-halifax-demonstration-1.5251221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fnova-scotia%2Fottawa-urged-to-support-hong-kong-protesters-at-halifax-demonstration-1.5251221&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=8a68a749\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/ottawa-urged-to-support-hong-kong-protesters-at-halifax-demonstration-1.5251221</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Chronicle Herald亦已登報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thechronicleherald.ca/opinion/local-perspectives/commentary-please-hear-hong-kongs-cry-for-help-342065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thechronicleherald.ca%2Fopinion%2Flocal-perspectives%2Fcommentary-please-hear-hong-kongs-cry-for-help-342065%2F&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=06658125\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thechronicleherald.ca/opinion/local-perspectives/commentary-please-hear-hong-kongs-cry-for-help-342065/</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Coast 都有<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thecoast.ca/halifax/what-canada-can-do-to-help-the-hong-kong-protesters/Content?oid=22299410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecoast.ca%2Fhalifax%2Fwhat-canada-can-do-to-help-the-hong-kong-protesters%2FContent%3Foid%3D22299410&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=2a985afd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thecoast.ca/halifax/what-canada-can-do-to-help-the-hong-kong-protesters/Content?oid=22299410</a><br />\n<br />\n我地吾係G20亦吾係攬炒團隊，人微言輕，亦俾大陸人不停起底騷擾，但本住不為善少而不為嘅中旨決定繼續做落去。<br />\n<br />\n我預吿定我地已經plan左下一步行動，有update再講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不上加國議會，誓不罷休</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6fc7b86adeb66c030275b326a2390160d44a6ff0","tid":1486393,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1e523dbed4a8e46168b5ecb709ba61e2c16e46","tid":1486393,"uid":273293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4f49add6c106e358921a9784fa42db6e9d1bc5","tid":1486393,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:52:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823人鏈</span></span></strong>：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486119</a>"},{"pid":"1989d9ab522f2c5b39f78c8af1d5d60fbfd5520c","tid":1486393,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"eec416c1fd2dfa63f112ca13247d90c36808cc3c","tid":1486393,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,